{"type": "article", "id": 13504, "title": "Leica 限量版相机", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-14T07:46:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000301mu9WDS7erXLjkR64.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tLeica 最近发布两款限量版相机，Leica X Maroon 和 Leica D-LUX Rolling Stone。前者是日本大阪梅田阪急百货店开业十周年的纪念版，所以配色上和“阪急电铁”红棕色配色一致，限量 50 台；后者是《Rolling Stone》杂志创刊 100 期纪念版，他们请来了 10 位音乐家参与，处处彰显滚石精神，限量 20 台。不过，两款相机只在日本发售，<a href=\"http://us.leica-camera.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141255IGBO2ignaCKWAER7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141256qhKZlWAzgJtkIBVd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}